title: Tiny Oakland house moves up the block from hospital
text:
Photo: James Tensuan, Special To The Chronicle The house on 5204 Martin Luther King Jr. Way just barely clears the BART tracks on the way to its new home. The house on 5204 Martin Luther King Jr. Way just barely clears the...
At first light Sunday, the little house rolled off the corner lot where it had spent the last 81 years and took a hard left under the BART tracks.
